parameters: Combatant: "You startled me... Did some brat wander in here...?"
Yui: "Why is there a combatant in a place like this?"

Combatant: "Little lady, this area is off-limits to unauthorized
personnel."
Combatant: "Now that you know, I can't let you leave."

Combatant: "Maybe I'll lock you up underground and you can become our
plaything. Hehehe."

Combatant: "Yeah, that's right. You'll never see the light of day
again."
Yui: "Thanks for telling me! So your hideout is underground, huh?"
Yui: "Well then, I guess it's time for me to take you guys down!"
Combatant: "Hahaha, do you fancy yourself a hero, little lady?"

Combatant: "Even if you know that, there's nothing you can do about
it."
Yui: "Oh sacred light, grant me strength!"
